I want to ask about the mosquitoes.

00:19:29.679 --> 00:19:30.773
Okay.

00:19:30.773 --> 00:19:37.298
So, we have mosquitoes being released all over California by Google.

00:19:37.298 --> 00:19:45.969
They're planning to—yeah, they're planning to release millions of mosquitoes into California to help stop disease.

00:19:45.969 --> 00:19:47.380
Thanks, Google.

00:19:47.380 --> 00:19:58.880
I'm just curious if you know if they ever heard of malaria or West Nile or any of these other diseases.

00:19:58.880 --> 00:20:01.539
I wonder if that'll help them.

00:20:01.539 --> 00:20:10.070
Pretty smart, huh?

00:20:10.080 --> 00:20:14.319
Google wants to help us out with the ticks, you know, the ticks, whatever.

00:20:18.617 --> 00:20:20.400
You know, RFK said today there's more uptick in Lyme disease across the nation than there's been in—they don't know when.

00:20:20.400 --> 00:20:30.526
And so they all of a sudden have a new shot for you to take for Lyme disease.

00:20:32.983 --> 00:20:33.780
They created it for ticks because these ticks are spreading so bad.

00:20:33.780 --> 00:20:36.662
We're going to have a new tick shot.

00:20:36.662 --> 00:20:39.863
So, they got a new tick shot for you.

00:20:39.863 --> 00:20:44.183
Like COVID, you can get that with your booster for your COVID shot.

00:20:44.183 --> 00:20:44.731
Yeah.

00:20:44.731 --> 00:20:45.486
Go ahead.

00:20:45.486 --> 00:20:47.886
So, is this vaccine available now?

